{"tid":99871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國少年獵殺250kg野豬　破維州紀錄","createTime":"2017-01-29T14:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T11:03:53.000Z","uid":33936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9128eeae7cac59b2511f217bed219d596177bc","tid":99871,"uid":33936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"美國維珍尼亞州一名少年，日前在家中後院發現一隻超巨型黑豬闖入，慣於狩獵的他立即提起步槍，到後院驅趕巨豬。最終少年射殺該隻巨豬後，始發現牠足足有近250公斤重、2米長，可能是維珍尼亞州史上最大頭野豬。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n17歲少年布里登（Jacob Breeden）上周發現該隻黑色雄豬，聲稱雄豬主動發起攻擊，他在別無選擇下將雄豬射殺。布里登指，當時感到非常驚慌，因外甥及姪兒均在屋內。當局正檢驗豬屍，以確定牠是有人飼養抑或野生；如屬野豬，便會打破該州的最巨型野豬紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道指，維珍尼亞州的野豬平均重量約為90公斤。生物學家戴伊表示，如果該豬是野生，相信牠生前獲大量餵食。雖然打獵被愛護動物人士譴責，但由於當地野豬經常破壞農作物，因此民眾可合法射殺牠們。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2iuolzx1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2iuolzx1&h=7d77d7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8kcha5bx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8kcha5bx&h=1da72c56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbffa39a43faf4f4f94d1f6043a49f6dfdb63b1d","tid":99871,"uid":33936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/mobile/bknint-20170129172005239-0129_17011_001.html#popupGallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170129%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170129172005239-0129_17011_001.html%23popupGallery&d=wuRAGhAhlQknfzdK5YHn85kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a7f93956\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170129/mobile/bknint-20170129172005239-0129_17011_001.html#popupGallery</a>"},{"pid":"3fd16b87f1f1fef3dd1d9028095e0917a2560be7","tid":99871,"uid":65832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"樓主同類受害有冇啲傷心嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6345deffd1aa3a413b6c71